'''豆蔻酰化'''（{{lang-en|'''Myristoylation'''}}）是一种[[蛋白质|蛋白质]][[翻译后修饰|翻译后修饰]]方式，豆蔻酰基[[官能团|基团]]来自于[[肉豆蔻酸|肉豆蔻酸]]，[[共价键|共价]]结合到肽链[[N-末端|N-末端]][[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]残基的α-[[氨基|氨基]]上<ref name="Lehninger Textbook">{{cite book|last=Cox|first=David L. Nelson, Michael M.|title=Lehninger principles of biochemistry|year=2005|publisher=W.H. Freeman|location=New York|isbn=978-0716743392|edition=4th|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/lehningerprincip00lehn_0}}</ref>。[[肉豆蔻酸|肉豆蔻酸]]是一种14-碳饱和脂肪酸(14:0) ，或称为“正十四烷酸”（''n''-Tetradecanoic acid）。豆蔻酰化这种[[翻译后修饰|翻译后修饰]]方式被称为“共翻译修饰”（co-translationally），在[[细胞质|细胞质]]中由[[N-豆蔻酰转移酶|N-豆蔻酰转移酶]]完成<ref name="Protein Lipidation">{{cite book|last=Tamanoi|first=edited by Fuyuhiko|title=Protein lipidation|year=2001|publisher=Academic Press|location=San Diego, CA|isbn=978-0-12-122722-7|edition=3rd|author2=Sigman, David S.}}</ref>，是最常见的脂肪酰化反应<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Mohammadzadeh|first1=Fatemeh|last2=Hosseini|first2=Vahid|last3=Mehdizadeh|first3=Amir|last4=Dani|first4=Christian|last5=Darabi|first5=Masoud|date=2018-11-30|title=A method for the gross analysis of global protein acylation by gas-liquid chromatography|journal=IUBMB Life|volume=71|issue=3|pages=340–346|language=en|doi=10.1002/iub.1975|pmid=30501005|issn=1521-6543|doi-access=free}}</ref>，普遍存在于各种[[真核生物|真核生物]]中<ref name="Kara Infection and Immunity">{{cite journal|last=Kara|first=UA|author2=Stenzel, DJ |author3=Ingram, LT |author4=Bushell, GR |author5=Lopez, JA |author6= Kidson, C |title=Inhibitory monoclonal antibody against a (myristylated) small-molecular-weight antigen from Plasmodium falciparum associated with the parasitophorous vacuole membrane.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_infection-and-immunity_1988-04_56_4/page/903|journal=Infection and Immunity|date=Apr 1988|volume=56|issue=4|pages=903–9|doi=10.1128/IAI.56.4.903-909.1988|pmid=3278984 |pmc=259388}}</ref>，与[[蛋白質交互作用|蛋白-蛋白相互作用]]、蛋白-脂质相互作用有关<ref name="Biology and Enzymology of Myristoylation">{{cite journal|last=Farazi|first=T. A.|title=The Biology and Enzymology of Protein N-Myristoylation|journal=Journal of Biological Chemistry|date=29 August 2001|volume=276|issue=43|pages=39501–39504|doi=10.1074/jbc.R100042200|pmid=11527981|doi-access=free}}</ref>。
